(301, 1, '2018-09-05 08:25:34', '2018-09-05 08:25:34', '<p><span style=\"color: #000000\">We are seeking for a&nbsp; self-motivated sales executive to join our growing company. In this position, you will be responsible for pursuing sales opportunities through traditional channels to reach new prospects. Strong interpersonal skills and a customer-focused approach are a must.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">We want a Sales Hunter in you – this is a new business acquisition position. You must exhibit excellent business generation skills as well as an organized approach to sales development, proactively. We expect you to be very professional with high energy level and hungry personality. If you think above doesn’t describe you, DO NOT read further.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\">CHROME primarily works in core software development and other related goods. This includes websites, domain and web hosting. You will act as Business Development Officer to increase sales of web hosting packages specifically; and other products in general.<br /></span></p><p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><b>Sales Executive Duties and Responsibilities:</b></span></p><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Actively seek out new sales opportunities through cold calling, networking, and social media</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Listen and draw out the concerns/problems of customers to identify possible solutions.</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Identify the traits of the ideal customer and seek to find others with the same traits</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Conduct market research to identify selling possibilities and evaluate customer needs</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Set up meetings with potential clients</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Prepare and deliver presentations on products/services</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Prepare and report on goals, sales, and prospects</span></li><li><span style=\"color: #000000\">Negotiate and close deals; handle complaints or objections</span></li></ul><p></p><p></p>', 'Tele-Sales Executive', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tele-sales-executive', '', '', '2018-09-05 08:25:34', '2018-09-05 08:25:34', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&amp;p=301', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
(304, 1, '2018-09-05 10:12:14', '2018-09-05 10:12:14', '<span style=\"color: #000000;\">We are a germany Based BPO looking for young, Bright and Ambitious Male/Female Customer Services Executives to join our friendly and exciting call center</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Peakstel is here to change the stereotype of call centre industry. We required candidates who put their work before anything else and want to grow and achieve something in their life. If you want to stand out of the crowd and are ready for that chance to bring about a change in your life, now is the time for you</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Peakstel is offering handsome salary packages to deserving candidates. Everyone is encouraged to apply for the job with a positive attitude to polish themselves and enable themselves to get to the top. Best environment and staff will be provided the the candidates. Our aim is to not only hire people but to make them think out of the box to get what they dreamt of.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b>Requirements:</b></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Outbound Call Center Temp to hire position Hours: Monday - Friday, 8PM – 5AM </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Responsibilities will include but are not limited to: </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Providing outstanding customer service to all customers in a professional and courteous manner </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Data and order entry </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Handling a high volume of outbound calls </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Reaching out to customers regarding orders, deliveries, inquires, etc. Requirements: </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clear and professional speaking voice/telephone manner </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Excellent customer service skills </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bilingual a plus </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Proficiency in basic PC applications and MS Word, Excel and Outlook </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ability to perform basic math skills </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Problem solving skills </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Excellent attention to detail </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sound decision making skills </span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Work well in a team environment </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Fresh candidates:  15K-20K basic depending upon caliber.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Experience Candidates: 25K-45K Basic depending on experience/skills.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">If you have what it takes to be a part of our success then we are looking forward to hear from you.</span>', 'Customer Service Representative', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'customer-service-representative', '', '', '2019-04-07 03:57:20', '2019-04-07 03:57:20', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&#038;p=304', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
(312, 1, '2018-09-05 11:50:03', '2018-09-05 11:50:03', '<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Akara Paints Pakistan Limited, a leading paint manufacturing company is looking For “RMS Officer” in Lahore.To arrange the Short Packing Materials in advance as per requirement with the coordination, and to plan for maintaining the maximum and minimum stock level as per requirement.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Update the Bin Cards of all Raw Materials &amp; empty gelatin capsles on daily basis and keep all records from time to time.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Major responsibilities may include.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Responsible for timely receiving of finished goods in warehouse and total number of move orders received should be transferred with material within prescribed time after receiving.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Responsible for placement of material in shelves and accurate picking of material according to pick slips in order to reduce mismatches.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Responsible to inspect physical conditions of equipment its maintenance, repairs, or replacements.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Responsible for ensuring safety and security of material and equipment</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Skills:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Oracle ERP</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Candidate with at least 2 years relevant experience as Storekeeper in a in a Reputed Company. Must have experience in Mumbai Based RMC Companies. Can Join Immediately. Computer Knowledge is must. Excellent Communication &amp; Coordination Skills.</span>', 'Raw Material Store Officer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'raw-material-store-officer', '', '', '2019-04-07 04:07:30', '2019-04-07 04:07:30', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&#038;p=312', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
(314, 1, '2018-09-05 12:17:28', '2018-09-05 12:17:28', '<b>MISSION AND PRINCIPAL ACTIVIES</b>\r\n\r\n<b>Attendance and involvement at work:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Observe the MSF charter.</li>\r\n 	<li>Perform all activity in line with the MSF protocols and procedures.</li>\r\n 	<li>Respect the time schedule and be at work on time (flexible at anytime).</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintain good relationship with other team members.</li>\r\n 	<li>Adhere to MSF Hygiene and Sterilization protocols.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>1. Application of basic hygiene rules</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Respects the clean and dirty circuits.</li>\r\n 	<li>When at work, the sterilization technician wears surgical scrubs, cap, mask,and non-sterile gloves.</li>\r\n 	<li>Clean and disinfect work equipment and surfaces.</li>\r\n 	<li>Ensuring the cleanless of the sterilization room and the surroundings.</li>\r\n 	<li>Puts on clean set of above clothes each day.</li>\r\n 	<li>Performs <b>antiseptic</b> handwashing upon entering the room, and before handling equipment.</li>\r\n 	<li>Changes the clothes and shoes at IN and OUT.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>2. Description of tasks.</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Follow the standard precautions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Follow the schedule of tasks set for the service.</li>\r\n 	<li>Receives the dirty medical devices from Operation Theatre and other clinicaldepartments.</li>\r\n 	<li>Pre-disinfect and clean soiled medical devices.</li>\r\n 	<li>Check and pack devices taking note in event of damage or incomplete set.</li>\r\n 	<li>Check and fold the clean linen taking note in event of damage, incomplete setor low quality of laundry procedure.</li>\r\n 	<li>Steam sterilizes devices as indicated following strictly the MSF protocol.</li>\r\n 	<li>Monitor the effectiveness of thesterilization cycle taking note at register.</li>\r\n 	<li>Identify each sterilized packaccording to the respective wards in the register book.</li>\r\n 	<li>Store and managed the sterilizeddevices.</li>\r\n 	<li>Distribute the sterilizeddevices to respective departments.</li>\r\n 	<li>Participate in inventory ofequipment and materials.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>3. Training:</b>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Participating in on-goingpersonnel training (sterilization, hygiene etc.)</li>\r\n 	<li>Participating in medicalmeetings,monthly and when necessary.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<b>4. Other</b>:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li> Inform direct supervisor inevent of error without delay</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Sterilization Technician', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sterilization-technician', '', '', '2019-04-07 04:17:45', '2019-04-07 04:17:45', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&#038;p=314', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
(315, 1, '2018-09-05 12:36:59', '2018-09-05 12:36:59', '<span style=\"color: #000000;\">To improve existing product The R&amp;D Manager at  driving strong, profitable same store sales results through assisting in the development of new products and ingredients as well as ensuring the quality of existing items. A successful candidate will have experience successfully implementing the product development process from innovation to commercialisation and have a strong understanding of technical documents with the ability to communicate and solve ingredient quality issues.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><b>RESPONSIBILITIES</b></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Applies understanding and knowledge of consumer, market and industry trends in developing compelling core and promotional menu offerings that drive guest satisfaction, guest traffic and brand awareness while meeting Nekter’s financial requirements.</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Manage and problem solve and manage all aspects of new and existing menu development. This will include but not limited to: recipes, nutrition requirements, yields, in-store procedures and smallwares.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Analyze and study competition, direct and non-direct, to ensure that we are staying current with industry trends at the same time introducing initiatives that put us above and first with our customers and competition.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Create a pipeline of new items developed, approved and tested ready to be implemented as needed.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Supported technically the local teams for new product development, adaptation and transfer of international innovations.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Involved in costing of new and existing products.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">In depth market understanding and competitor intelligence in the region.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Trained the local teams on best practices in sensory analysis .</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To initiate and active involvement in new product development (NPD) using advice and information from the quality, sales, marketing &amp; operations departments as inputs.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To conduct the study on shelf life of newly developing product to offer quality product to our customer.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ensuring raw Materials, Pre-Mixes, in process Material, Packaging Material and finished Goods needed for new products are in place for the work to be carried out.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">To ensure all records are maintained with proper back up and presented to the management.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ensuring new products conforms the standards and advice QC in setting HACCP for new products.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Performed lead role in setting and establishing a proper R&amp;D department and perform other duties as per the further expansion of the department.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Check audit reports to ensure daily opening &amp; closing balance of all raw and packaging material to avoid difference in the monthly audit.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Senior Web Developer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-web-developer', '', '', '2019-04-07 04:13:28', '2019-04-07 04:13:28', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&#038;p=315', 0, 'job_post', '', 0),
(317, 1, '2018-09-06 09:54:21', '2018-09-06 09:54:21', '<span style=\"color: #000000;\">We are seeking IT Teacher for our intistution that Provides instruction in selected areas of Information Technology to ensure that students gain appropriate knowledge and skills about the industry and are prepared for a career and post-secondary opportunities</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">Provides content-related and appropriate instruction based on state and local curriculum through a combination of classroom, laboratory, and co-curricular experiences, community-based instruction and projects based on program guidelines and requirements,leadership opportunities for students by establishing a Career and Technical Student Organization (CTSO), i.e. SkillsUSA or TSA, as a co-curricular instructional tool within the classroom Manages and maintains program facilities and equipment Adheres to all state guidelines required for the implementation of a successful program</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Candidates must be BS/BE/BCS/MCS/MS from any recognized university.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Having good conceptual knowledge of object oriented programming, HTML, JavaScript/VB Script, SQL Server , Java and good exposure to C#, ASP.net, Winforms, Webforms and RDBMS.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Knowledge of Open Source Technology (PHP, MySql, Linux etc) will be an advantage.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Good teaching and communication skills. Only serious and Full time candidates should apply. No part timers are required.</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">NED, KU, SSUET candidates will be given preference</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Looking for Manager IT Faculty', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'looking-for-manager-it-faculty', '', '', '2019-04-07 04:01:51', '2019-04-07 04:01:51', '', 0, 'https://demo.nokriwp.com/?post_type=job_post&#038;p=317', 0, 'jo